title: RAK13101 WisBlock GSM/GPRS Module Datasheet > RAK13101 WisBlock GSM/GPRS Module Datasheet > Overview > Description > Introduction to WisBlock RAK13101 GSM/GPRS Module
content: **WisBlock RAK13101 GSM/GPRS Module** is a part of the WisBlock Wireless series that provides GSM/GPRS capability on the WisBlock platform by using Quectel MC20CE cellular module.
parent_content: **WisBlock RAK13101 GSM/GPRS Module** is a part of the WisBlock Wireless series that provides GSM/GPRS capability on the WisBlock platform by using Quectel MC20CE cellular module.

title: RAK13101 WisBlock GSM/GPRS Module Datasheet > RAK13101 WisBlock GSM/GPRS Module Datasheet > Specifications > Overview > RAK13101 Mounting Mechanism on WisBlock Base Module
content:
The RAK13101 module can be mounted on the IO slot of the WisBlock Base board. Figure 1 shows the mounting mechanism of the RAK13101 on a WisBlock Base module, such as a RAK5005-O.  
> **Image:** RAK13101 mounting mechanism on a WisBlock Base module
